                (LTrim
                <ol>
                    <li>Turn on the option in the config UI</li>
                    <li>Place the icons (<code>ico</code>/<code>png</code>/<code>jpeg</code>) in the same folder as <code>MicMute.exe</code></li>
                    <li>
                        Rename them as:
                        <ul>
                            <li>
